(a) Optical conductivity (σ1) spectra of a-C films on ITO substrate. (b) The estimated spectral-weight-transfer (SWT) over three energy ranges: 0.62–1.00 eV (W1), 1.00–4.00 eV (W2), 4.00–5.62 eV (W3). W = W1 + W2 + W3.

